en_179953_0	A 22-year-old youth was arrested by Chilaw Police for allegedly clubbing a father of 4 to death.
en_179953_1	The victim was M. Sugandharaman, who was aged 56 years.
en_179953_2	The incident took place at around 5.30 pm yesterday (Jan. 01).
en_179953_3	After the incident, the victim had come home and gone to sleep.
en_179953_4	Police said he had died in sleep.
